text: Canadaway Creek is a stream in Chautauqua County, New York which empties into Lake Erie in Dunkirk, New York. Non-natives settled on the creek first in 1804, in what was first called "Canadaway" and became Fredonia, New York. ==References== Category:Rivers of Chautauqua County, New York Category:Tributaries of Lake Erie
title: Canadaway Creek
